      • sanitizeFileFolderNames

        public static String sanitizeFileFolderNames(String input)
        As there are certain characters which are not allowed in alfresco as file and folder names, we need to replace those charasters with "_" chars < (less than), > (greater than), : (colon), " (double quote), / (forward slash), \ (backslash), | (vertical bar or pipe), ? (question mark), * (asterisk)
        Returns:
        sanitized string after replacing the invalid chars with all "_", and trimming its length to 254
